          We offer fast, easy, and affordable PCC services for individuals and corporate clients. We also have a strong network of professionals who are native speakers and can assist with document attestation, verification, translation, delivery, and follow-up. Want to know more? Call us today for a free consultation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Index list -->
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:52px;" class="two-col">
      {whyIndex.map(point => (
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;">
